Pretend I'm not even here.

56
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,279
Pretend I'm nothing.

57
00:03:14,799 --> 00:03:15,959
What is this about?

58
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:18,080
You said

59
00:03:18,239 --> 00:03:19,440
you liked my canine.

60
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:20,880
I didn't!

61
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:23,920
I remember

62
00:03:24,119 --> 00:03:25,440
reading about it here.

63
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,719
Cut it out!

64
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,320
You're driving me crazy!

65
00:03:31,959 --> 00:03:32,679
I was just...

66
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:33,679
You want to preserve

67
00:03:33,839 --> 00:03:34,799
the evidence

68
00:03:34,999 --> 00:03:36,200
and have me locked up.

69
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,440
I'm still young.

70
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:40,640
Have mercy on me.

71
