75
00:03:47,399 --> 00:03:48,080
you read.

76
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,999
Please.

77
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,880
I just find you cute.

78
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,559
I...

79
00:04:03,519 --> 00:04:05,080
I didn't mean it.

80
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,600
Sorry!

81
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:11,239
Xu Jingjing.

82
00:04:12,559 --> 00:04:13,559
You know how it goes

83
00:04:13,839 --> 00:04:14,600
in those dramas.

84
00:04:14,959 --> 00:04:15,999
This must be a dream.

85
00:04:16,719 --> 00:04:17,560
Wake up, Xu Jingjing.

86
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,039
Wake up!

87
00:04:53,359 --> 00:04:54,120
It's my fault.

88
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,519
I shouldn't have

89
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,680
taken your notebook.

90
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,200
My curiosity got

91
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:01,080
the better of me.

92
00:05:03,359 --> 00:05:04,279
I thought your words

93
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,240
and doodles

94
00:05:05,479 --> 00:05:06,200
were interesting.

95
00:05:07,159 --> 00:05:07,719
You know me

96
00:05:07,919 --> 00:05:09,000
better than I know myself.

97
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,200
Read this.

98
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:15,359
Gaogao's favorite drink

99
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,839
is matcha red bean milktea.

100
00:05:17,159 --> 00:05:17,800
He finishes

101
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,440
the red beans of the drink.

102
00:05:20,159 --> 00:05:20,640
I thought

103
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,880
I loved matcha.

104
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:23,479
But it was the red beans.

105
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,680
Stop reading.

106
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,560
Stop it

107
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,399
or I'll end my life here.

108
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:31,680
And read this.

109
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,320
Gaogao read another

110
00:05:33,479 --> 00:05:34,279
book written

111
