by Agatha Christie

112
00:05:35,919 --> 00:05:36,479
in the library.

113
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:37,200
So, he prefers

114
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:37,919
detective novels.

115
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,800
I thought

116
00:05:38,959 --> 00:05:40,159
I prefer historical thrillers.

117
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,120
This is my stop.

118
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:57,680
Here you go.

119
00:06:02,919 --> 00:06:03,680
Thanks.

120
00:06:04,159 --> 00:06:04,919
I should get going.

121
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:07,560
Xu Jingjing.

122
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,719
Which university are you enrolling in?

123
