146
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:34,320
Come on.

147
00:08:34,599 --> 00:08:35,440
Excuse me.

148
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:36,639
How is it?

149
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,639
I didn't make it.

150
00:08:37,839 --> 00:08:38,479
