151
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,239
Me neither.

152
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,080
Great!

153
00:08:42,119 --> 00:08:43,239
I'm not doing it.

154
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:45,920
My Yaoyao!

155
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,200
Yaoyao.

156
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,440
See you at university.

157
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,719
Don't be silly.

158
00:08:51,119 --> 00:08:52,119
