159
00:08:54,119 --> 00:08:55,639
No!

160
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,479
Jingjing, did you make it?

161
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,839
I'm too scared to find out.

162
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:01,879
I'll check for you.

163
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:06,719
Xu Jingjing!

164
00:09:06,999 --> 00:09:07,440
You made it!

165
00:09:07,719 --> 00:09:08,879
You made it too!

166
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:10,759
I made it!

167
00:09:11,239 --> 00:09:11,959
We're in the same class!

168
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,759
What about Xiaobai?

169
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,119
Don't bother, Jingjing.

170
00:09:20,599 --> 00:09:21,440
I didn't make it.

171
00:09:23,759 --> 00:09:24,400
That's normal.

172
00:09:25,239 --> 00:09:26,680
