177
00:09:39,719 --> 00:09:40,359
Alright.

178
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:43,479
We'll be there for you.
Don't cry.

179
00:09:45,599 --> 00:09:47,639
We can still meet.

180
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:48,959
Yeah, that's right.

181
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:50,759
- Don't cry.
- Hush.

182
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:51,719
Don't cry.

183
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:53,320
Little crybaby.

184
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,160
Come in.

185
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:00,800
Principal.

186
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:01,839
You asked for me.

187
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:02,999
Mr. Zhao.

188
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,599
Sit down.

189
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,400
Sure.

190
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,040
You submitted

191
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,040
the proposal for

192
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:09,999
the TV program.

193
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,359
We've gone through it.

194
00:10:12,239 --> 00:10:12,999
The final exam

195
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,959
