196
00:10:14,479 --> 00:10:15,080
I think

197
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,560
it's time for everyone to relax.

198
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,560
That's great.

199
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:18,520
Thanks, Principal Shen.

200
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:19,759
I'll contact them at once.

201
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:21,440
Mr. Zhao, hold on.

202
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,400
I need to ask.

203
00:10:23,599 --> 00:10:24,200
What is it?

204
00:10:25,239 --> 00:10:27,080
Can I participate as well?

205
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:30,800
I'd love to join too.

206
00:10:31,359 --> 00:10:32,400
Sure thing, Principal.

207
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:33,920
I'll give him a call.

208
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,400
- Sure.
- Thanks, Principal.

209
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,200
Thank you.

210
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,599
Seriously?

211
00:10:37,999 --> 00:10:39,639
Breaking news right
before the summer break.

212
00:10:39,959 --> 00:10:40,400
Our school agreed

213
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,599
to this TV program?

214
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,400
This is your chance

215
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:45,479
to talk to Gao Zhan.

216
00:10:45,999 --> 00:10:47,239
Read the letter you wrote.

217
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:49,080
How touching.

218
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,440
Look.

219
00:10:50,599 --> 00:10:51,800
He can't reject you

220
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,839
in front of the crowd.

221
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,599
I've been embarrassed enough.

222
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,080
This is a TV program.

223
00:10:56,239 --> 00:10:57,520
The whole country will watch it.

224
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,359
I'm not doing it.

225
00:10:58,560 --> 00:10:59,599
I'm pretty curious about it.

226
00:10:59,999 --> 00:11:01,719
Who would participate?

227
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,280
Certainly not me.

228
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,520
None of you are going?

229
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:05,839
I'm not going either, then.

230
00:11:05,959 --> 00:11:06,920
I'm joining.

231
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,800
Yaoyao, the rooftop is where...

232
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:10,680
Ni Dapeng.

233
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,119
I'm warning you.

234
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,879
If you utter my name

235
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:14,999
on the rooftop,

236
00:11:15,719 --> 00:11:17,400
I'll make your life a living hell,

237
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,320
got it?

238
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,119
Sure.

239
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,800
You have my words.

240
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:35,980
(I Want to Tell You Out Loud)

241
00:11:36,839 --> 00:11:38,119
Chen Bei!

242
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,719
(I Want to Tell You Out Loud)
Am I speaking loud enough?

243
00:11:53,759 --> 00:11:54,639
Grade 11 Class 3!

244
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,759
Ms. Chen Bei!

245
00:11:57,359 --> 00:11:57,999
Hey there!

246
00:11:58,999 --> 00:12:01,560
I am Zhao Donglin, the PE teacher!

247
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,639
I should drop the job title.

248
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,560
I'll just be Zhao Donglin.

249
00:12:10,359 --> 00:12:12,440
Grade 11 Class 3, Ms. Chen Bei!

250
00:12:13,639 --> 00:12:14,839
I am Zhao Donglin!

251
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,920
I have something to tell you.

252
00:12:18,599 --> 00:12:20,839
(I Want to Tell You Out Loud)
I really like you!

253
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,119
Zhao Donglin!

254
00:12:24,839 --> 00:12:25,639
Are you out of your mind?

255
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:26,959
Watch your step.

256
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:27,999
You could fall.

257
00:12:28,599 --> 00:12:29,920
What brings you here?

258
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,239
Are you really

259
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,359
going to say that tomorrow?

260
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,160
Yeah.

261
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:37,320
What's wrong?

262
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,879
No, you can't do it.

263
00:12:39,239 --> 00:12:39,800
Why not?

264
00:12:40,599 --> 00:12:41,959
The production team says I can say it

265
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,080
if I mean it.

266
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:50,260
(Ms. Chen Bei of Grade 11 Class 3)

267
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:56,599
Are you serious?

268
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:57,320
Yeah.

269
00:12:57,879 --> 00:12:58,479
I made up my mind

270
00:12:58,639 --> 00:12:59,400
when they came to me.

271
00:12:59,959 --> 00:13:01,080
That's not what I mean.

272
00:13:01,599 --> 00:13:02,400
What do you mean, then?

273
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:07,280
Do you mean it

274
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,280
when you say you like me?

275
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:12,520
Ms. Chen.

276
00:13:13,719 --> 00:13:14,879
I really like you.

277
00:13:16,119 --> 00:13:16,959
I like how you are kind

278
00:13:17,719 --> 00:13:18,479
and honest.

279
00:13:18,920 --> 00:13:20,280
I like your smile.

280
00:13:22,119 --> 00:13:22,999
I'd explode

281
00:13:23,239 --> 00:13:24,239
if you didn't let me say it.

282
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:26,239
So be it.

283
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:27,879
Do not say it.

284
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,440
If that's what you want,

285
00:13:33,119 --> 00:13:33,879
there is another way.

286
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:35,759
What is it?

287
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,280
Say yes now.

288
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,879
To what?

289
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,200
To be my girlfriend.

290
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:51,340
♪When my boldness turns to hesitation
because of you♪

291
00:13:53,020 --> 00:13:57,660
♪I can't let you go so I toss and turn♪

292
00:14:00,999 --> 00:14:03,759
So, we can only be colleagues?

293
00:14:06,239 --> 00:14:07,680
I'm counting on you.

294
00:14:07,999 --> 00:14:08,560
Is that a yes?

295
